after a long illness.
</P>
<P>
	   Pavarotti canceled at the last minute because he was not feeling well, the
opera house said. Also missing were Bayo and Vargas.
</P>
<P>
	   The audience wasn't in a forgiving mood. Many booed loud and long when the
three absences were announced, delaying the concert for nearly an hour. About
200 spectators stormed out, shouting "Kraus never deserved this."
