	   ------
</P>
<P>
	   NBC's "Meet the Press" -- Topic: Campaign 2000. Guests: Sen. Judd Gregg,
R-N.H.; Reps. Lindsey Graham, R-S.C., and Jerrold Nadler, D-N.Y.; and Bob Shrum
of the Gore campaign. Topic: Gays in the Military. Guests: retired Gen. John
