	   CNN's "Late Edition" -- Topic: Bradley vs. Gore. Guests: Sens. Paul
Wellstone, D-Minn., and Tom Harkin, D-Iowa. Topic: Hillary Clinton's Senate bid.
Guests: Former New York City Mayor Ed Koch and former Rep. Susan Molinari,
R-N.Y. Topics: Russia and the Middle East. Guest: Richard Holbrook, U.S.
ambassador to the United Nations.
</P>
<P>
	   ------
</P>
<P>
	   "Fox News Sunday" -- Topic: Campaign 2000. Guests: Bill Bradley, Democratic
presidential contender, and David Yepsen of the Des Moines Register.
</P>
